[302540.828457, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[38;5;174m│\u001b[39m   \u001b[6G \u001b[38;5;246mFable 5 · Claude Max · jessay@gmail.com's \u001b[39m     \u001b[2m\u001b[38;5;174m│\u001b[39m\u001b[22m Added a `/doctor` chec… \u001b[38;5;174m│\r\u001b[6C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mOrganization\u001b[56G\u001b[39m`/commit-push-pr`\u001b[74Gnow\u001b[78G…\r\u001b[13C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m~/clyffy/landing/study/t1/a\u001b[56G\u001b[3m/release-notes for more\r\u001b[1B\u001b[23m\u001b[38;5;174m╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[48;5;237m\u001b[38;5;239m❯ \u001b[38;5;231mAdd a pxpipe statusline indicator for Claude Code: create \u001b[39m                    \r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;231mstatusline-pxpipe.sh in the current directory following the pattern of the \u001b[39m   \r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;231mreference statusline-infisical.sh (also in this directory): green dot when \u001b[39m   \r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;231mthe pxpipe proxy at 127.0.0.1:47821 is up (real HTTP check), red dot when \u001b[39m    \r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;231mdown, plus tokens-saved-today if cheaply available from \u001b[39m                      \r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;231m~/.pxpipe/events.jsonl; keep it fast (<100ms) and show how it would be wired \u001b[39m \r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;231minto settings.json alongside the existing statusline (do not modify anything \u001b[39m \r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;231min ~/.claude). Done = script runs correctly in both proxy-up and proxy-down \u001b[39m  \r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;231mstate\u001b[39m                                                                         \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[49m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;174m*\u001b[3GPrestidigitating… \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;37m──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[48;5;37m\u001b[38;5;16m study-t1-stock \u001b[